<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٦٩٩٤ - ٢٣٣٢ - <span class="c2">«هذا خالي فليرني امرؤ خاله»</span> .<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
